Package: KefiR
Title: Statistical Analysis with ANOVA, MANOVA, ANCOVA and Mixed Models
Version: 0.0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Antoine",
           family = "MassÃ©",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "antoine.masse@u-bordeaux.fr")
Description: Comprehensive statistical analysis pipeline for ANOVA, MANOVA,
    ANCOVA, and mixed models with automatic assumption checking, robust
    alternatives, post-hoc tests with visual representations, and reproducible
    code generation. Designed for researchers and students needing rigorous
    statistical analysis with pedagogical support.
